atrices are not viable and should be\navoided in the first place when constructing nuclear energy density functionals\nthat are eventually meant to be used in multi-reference calculations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Sep 2008 16:25:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 4 Mar 2009 17:22:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-29"}
